<h1>Thanks <%=@user.full_name %>!</h1>

<p>Thanks for purchasing some of our stuff! We hope you'll enjoy the shoes. So many shoes.</p>

<h2>Order ID: #<%= @order.id %></h2>
Unique Order Link: <%= link_to visitor_order_url(@order.unique_url),  visitor_order_url(@order.unique_url) %>
<h3>You bought:</h3>
<ul>
  <% @order.order_items.each do |oi| %>
  <li><%= oi.product.title %> (<%= oi.quantity %>)</li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>and you spent</p>
<h3><%= number_to_currency(@order.total_price) %></h3>

<p>Whoa! Watch it big spender.</p>
